headline: Assessing General Motors Valuation After Amazon Begins Testing BrightDrop Electric Vans
summary: Trying to figure out what to do with your General Motors shares, or maybe deciding whether now is the time to start your position? Let’s dig into what’s been happening and where things could be headed. GM’s stock closed at $61.24, marking some impressive moves lately: up 3.8% over the past week, 4.5% in the past month, and a strong 19.2% gain year-to-date.
